-- Lockheed gets $1.4 billion US launch contract
-- 
-- Fri Jun 27, 2008 5:43pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/06/27/us-lockheed-usa-space-idUSN2726057420080627

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - Lockheed Martin Corp ( LMT.N ) has received a $1.38 billion U.S. Air Force contract modification to extend government and military launch services through September 30, 2009, the Defense Department said Friday. 

 The deal also incorporates a one-year option for fiscal 2010, the Pentagon said in its daily contract digest. A spokeswoman for United Launch Alliance, a joint venture between Boeing Co ( BA.N ) and Lockheed Martin, did not immediately return a phone call seeking comment. (Reporting by  Jim Wolf ; Editing by  Andre Grenon )